<i>noun</i>: 소요 [소요], 소란 [소란], 소동 [소동], 분탕질 [분탕질] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>소요 [소요]</dt><br>
<dd>disturbance; commotion; agitation; riot</dd><br>
<dd>여러 사람이 시끄럽게 들고일어남. 또는 그런 소란.</dd><br>
<dd>A loud protest caused by a group of people, or such a disturbance.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>소란 [소란]</dt><br>
<dd>disturbance; fuss; commotion</dd><br>
<dd>시끄럽고 정신없게 복잡함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being noisy and hectic.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>소동 [소동]</dt><br>
<dd>disturbance; fuss; commotion</dd><br>
<dd>시끄럽게 떠들고 어지럽게 행동하는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of making a loud noise and causing a commotion.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>분탕질 [분탕질]</dt><br>
<dd>1. squandering; dissipating</dd><br>
<dd>집안의 재산을 모두 없애 버리는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of wastefully spending all of a household's wealth.</dd><br>
<dd>2. disturbance; commotion</dd><br>
<dd>시끄럽게 떠들며 소동을 일으키는 짓.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of causing a loud, noisy commotion.</dd><br>
<dd>3. robbery</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 쳐들어가서 재물을 빼앗거나 훔치는 짓.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) The act of invading and taking or stealing others' property.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>